data.description: Welcome to your new home at 10303 Fairington Ridge Cir in the vibrant community of Lithonia, GA! Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this charming condo offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience.    Step inside to discover an inviting open floor plan that effortlessly merges style with functionality. With 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, there's ample room for relaxation and rejuvenation. There is a storage area available outside of the condo as well. Parking is unassigned.    But that's not all – this condo has been thoughtfully upgraded with new LVP floors throughout, adding a touch of luxury to every step you take. Say goodbye to carpet woes and hello to easy maintenance and timeless elegance.
